1850
01:25:09,121 --> 01:25:10,679
Nos vemos, Malcolm.

1851
01:25:12,161 --> 01:25:13,230
Tú...

1852
01:25:13,361 --> 01:25:14,840
...repites...

1853
01:25:14,961 --> 01:25:17,236
...una sola palabra
de las que oíste aquí...

1854
01:25:17,361 --> 01:25:20,717
...y te amputaré la pierna. Te--

1855
